------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Ultimate Justice is a fan-made crossover between two series: Ace Attorney and Danganronpa. It will follow the lawyers of the Wright Anything Agency as they defend students of Hope’s Peak in various murder cases.

For more information, go to: https://aaultimatejustice.carrd.co/
